=======================================
Matrix Views (Referencing Matrix Parts)                                 [TOC]
=======================================
Referencing matrix parts and using these parts like regular matrices is a
common need in numerical software development.  In FLENS we call references
to matrix parts _views_.  You can use a matrix view like a normal matrix.  The
only difference is that when you create a matrix view no extra memory gets
allocated.


